1. Danas* je veoma lep dan. (Today is a very nice day.)
2. On je danas* otišao u šetnju. (He went for a walk today.)
3. Nastavili smo zabavu danas* uveče. (We continued the party tonight.)
4. Danas* je najbolji dan za odlazak. (Today is the best day to leave.)
5. Moj prijatelj je stigao iz inostranstva danas*. (My friend arrived from abroad today.)